Apex Legends is a battle royale set in the Titanfall universe. The action takes place 30 years after the war between the corporation and the militia, now the colonized worlds lie in ruins and warring factions reign on them. But the days of bloody massacres are over, now disputes are resolved in a game called Apex, where the winners receive glory and honor. Since Apex Legends is a hero shooter similar to Overwatch, you will need to choose who you want to play as before starting the battle. Legends, as the characters are called here, are divided into five classes: assault, clash, reconnaissance, support and control. In almost every group, at first only 1-2 characters out of 4 or more belonging to this class are open. For example, of the attack aircraft, only Bangalore is available, which can run fast and throw smoke bombs, and also carry out carpet bombing. If you want to play for someone else, you will have to farm legend tokens or, if you donâ€™t want to do this, buy Apex Legends coins and purchase the desired hero with them. Then you wonâ€™t need to play hundreds of matches on some Gibraltar or Bloodhound to increase your account level and get tokens for it. Instantly unlock Mad Maggie and bombard your enemies with rebellion drills and balls, or unlock control class legends, like Rampart with the Sheila machine gun, or Catalyst, who uses spikes.

Once you've played most of the characters, you'll definitely have one or more favorites. Although the game is made in first person, you will still often see your hero in the lobby while looking for opponents. And so that you donâ€™t get bored with his appearance, there are many skins in the game: some simply recolor the basic suit, while others completely change it. We offer you to buy Apex Legends coins and look into the game store, where you will find many sets with skins for the hero and weapons, as well as holograms and frames.

If you haven't deleted Apex Legends after a couple of games and continue to play, then it won't hurt you to purchase a premium battle pass. To do this, just buy Apex Legends coins and use them to unlock the battle pass, after which you will immediately receive a bonus to experience and unlock several heroes. In addition, as you progress through the levels, you will be able to collect rewards, including valuable metals, legend tokens and, of course, skins.

Whatever you need Apex Legends coins for, you can buy them on our marketplace, and the security system will ensure that the transaction goes perfectly. All you have to do is place an order, and after you receive the coins, confirm its completion. While the seller is fulfilling your order, the money will be protected by the security system; when you close the deal, it will automatically send the funds to the seller.

How to buy Apex Legends coins

  1. Select an offer and contact the seller.
  2. Place your order.
  3. Receive coins and confirm the order completion.

For sellers

Games such as Apex do not force players to donate, but they hint at it in every possible way. You can play like this, but only on a few characters that are open initially. Everything else: new heroes, skins, premiums are bought for coins, so some players prefer to donate for a comfortable game. On FunPay you can sell Apex Legends coins and make money on the difference in price; to do this, you need to become a seller by passing a rules knowledge test.
